headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Thinks Norwegian Cruise Line Stock Is Going to $30. Is It a Buy Around $20?
summary: One Wall Street analyst thinks investors can book some nice profits by investing in Norwegian Cruise Line (NYSE: NCLH) stock right now.  Uncertainty surrounding tariffs and interest rates has investors concerned about consumer spending.  While airlines have been warning investors in recent weeks that they are seeing a slowdown in both consumer and business travel, Boss thinks the concerns may not apply to cruise names like Norwegian.
